data.description: Welcome to 274 Green Knoll Lane~ Second floor ranch with over 1500 square feet! Private End Unit with  3 Bedrooms, 2 full baths with in-unit laundry!  Updated kitchen with newer cabinets, granite counters, back splash, stainless steel appliances, large pantry / closet along with space for a kitchen table.  Spacious Family Room featuring vaulted ceilings, gas fireplace,  tons of windows for all of that natural light with private access to a deck~ perfect for that morning coffee or evening grilling. Large Master Bedroom with two closets and ensuite master bath! Two nice sized secondary bedrooms.  Updated secondary full bath with linen closet.  Laundry room complete with washer and dryer. New Roof was installed in 2023.  Newer furnace and A/C.  Subdivision is complete with a Pool and Clubhouse!
